[3] Viet Nam
Date: Mon 15 Jun 2009
Source: Thanh Nien News [edited]
<http://www.thanhniennews.com/healthy/?catid=8&newsid=49830>


Over 21 000 dengue fever cases reported
---------------------------------------
More than 21 000 people in Viet Nam have contracted dengue fever so
far this year [2009], and 20 have died, according to reports from the
National Institute of Epidemiology and Pasteur institutes across the
country.

The figures show a 46.7 percent increase year-on-year, and the number
of people dying of the mosquito-borne illness is 4 more than the same
period last year [2008]. [According to PRO/MBDS posting Dengue - Viet
Nam (05) 20080612.1865 from 12 Jun 2008, at that time there was
mention of 11 deaths attributable to dengue during the 1st 5 months of
2008, and in a follow up posting on 25 Jun 2008 Dengue - Viet Nam (06)
20080625.1962 there was mention of 20 deaths attributable to dengue as
of 25 Jun 2008. - Mod.MPP]

According to the Hanoi Healthcare Preventative Center, the capital
city is facing a potential outbreak of the disease with 80 cases
reported so far this year [2009].

Meanwhile, the Ministry of Health said the epidemic will continue in
the south, as rain combined with hot, humid weather creates
conditions for mosquitoes to flourish.

--
Communicated by:
ProMED-MBDS Rapporteur Vern Weitzel

[The number of reported cases of dengue fever and dengue hemorrhagic
fever (DF/DHF) in the Western Pacific Region, by country in 2009, is
available at the WHO Western Pacific Region summary of cases updated
15 Jun
2009(<http://www.wpro.who.int/NR/rdonlyres/3C44FCF3-78D2-4655-BBEC-046DC7E2BCBB/0/Dengue_WPRO_2009_300409.pdf>
showing 16 655 cases and 14 deaths from DEN-1, DEN-2 & DEN-3 in Viet Nam.
- Sr. Tech. Ed. MJ]

[In 2008, 12 064 cases and 11 deaths of dengue infections had been
reported in Viet Nam by 11 Jun 2008 (see prior PRO/MBDS posting Dengue
- Viet Nam (05) 20080612.1865), and 19 859 cases and 20 deaths of
dengue infection by 25 Jun 2008, mostly from the southern provinces
(see prior PRO/MBDS posting Dengue - Viet Nam (06) 20080625.1962).

For maps of Viet Nam with provinces, see
<http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/middle_east_and_asia/vietnam_admin01.jpg> and
